		<pubDate>Sun, 11 May 2014 19:33:50 +0000</pubDate>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://clockworktwist.com/?p=2258#comment-89</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[I do write a series :) The Carmine Rojas novella has a sequel coming. But I didn&#039;t plan so well as you did and the books aren&#039;t really super interconnected. I also didn&#039;t start on the sequel until I got a publisher for the first book.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I do write a series 🙂 The Carmine Rojas novella has a sequel coming. But I didn&#8217;t plan so well as you did and the books aren&#8217;t really super interconnected. I also didn&#8217;t start on the sequel until I got a publisher for the first book.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
